             was indicted for <rs id="t18070408-73-off424" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18070408-73-off424" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18070408-73-off424" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18070408-73-cd425" type="crimeDate">6th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18070408-73-off424 t18070408-73-cd425"></join>, a bag, value 6 d. a travelling case, value 48 s. eleven silver locks, value 5 s. 6 d. three pieces of ribbon, value 5 s. a pocket book, value 6 d. two seven shilling pieces and six halfpence
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18070408-73-victim631" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Wells
                  <interp inst="t18070408-73-victim631" type="surname" value="Wells"></interp>
